SUMMARY:MAISTR — Call #1
DESCRIPTION:Company Representatives: Dwayne Hyzak (CEO)\, Ryan Nelson (CFO & Treasurer)\nIssuer: MAIN STREET CAPITAL CORP (MAISTR)\nRoadshow: Call #1: 11:00AM ET / 10:00AM CT - https://www.netroadshow.com/events/login/LE9zwo49flYDLzGYuQmniTwc9r3y6PQSXAd\; Call #2: 1:00PM ET / 12:00PM CT - https://www.netroadshow.com/events/login/LE9zwo3hUbUvaolPRlAP2cO53c0QGCCAr1s\n\nDeal context:\nMain Street Capital Corporation\, a BBB- rated (S&P and Fitch) principal investment firm\, has mandated RBC Capital Markets\, J.P. Morgan\, SMBC Nikko\, and Truist Securities to arrange fixed income investor calls scheduled for Tuesday\, February 3rd\, 2026\, with a potential capital markets transaction to follow subject to market conditions. The deal is at the mandate stage with two investor call sessions scheduled at 11:00AM ET and 1:00PM ET\, featuring CEO Dwayne Hyzak and CFO Ryan Nelson\, with virtual presentations available through NetRoadshow. No specific deal size\, tenor\, or security type has been disclosed at this stage.
LOCATION:Conference Call
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR